Immerse yourself in the emotion conveyed by rubies and discover their fascinating transformation from minerals to jewels through the meticulous work of expert gemstones and jewelers.

Van Cleef & Arpels is delighted to welcome you back to the GEMS exhibition at the National Museum of Natural History in Paris!

